data.title: Marie Pinho & Stephen Hensley's Wedding Registry
data.meta_description: Visit the wedding registry of Anne-Marie Pinho and Stephen Hensley of Naugatuck, CT, at MyRegistry.com and celebrate them on their big day, Saturday, November 17, 2018.
data.text:
You’ll notice that Anne-Marie & Stephen have added items from Williams Sonoma, Amazon, Kohls.com, and Costco. That’s the beauty of having a registry at MyRegistry.com—our members can add items from literally any store!

Spot something nice? Click BUY THIS GIFT, and don’t worry if you’re redirected to another site. Just put the item in your cart and check out!

Need help? Reach us 7 days a week via Live Chat or by calling 201.886.1000
